Do not deploy unless the user explicitly asks.

Known accidental file:
$null

If $null appears inside repo, delete it using:

Get-ChildItem -Force | Where-Object { $_.Name -eq '$null' } | Remove-Item -Force

Never leave helper/debug files behind.

