============================================================
BUILD RULES
============================================================

Backend build:

cd backend
npm run build

Frontend build:

cd frontend
npm run build

Run only the build relevant to the touched area:
- Backend-only patch: backend build only.
- Frontend-only patch: frontend build only.
- Full-stack patch: both builds.

Build success does not mean UAT PASS.
Do not claim final PASS without manual/API verification.

